definition: to set/to fix/to determine/to decide/to order

sentences.english: She ordered gummi bears and a knife a couple hours ago.
sentences.chinese: 幾小時前預定了一些小熊軟糖和一把刀。

sentences.english: The number of jiffies that this process has been scheduled in user mode.
sentences.chinese: 瞬間的進程正在使用預定模式的數量。

sentences.english: This helps the doctor estimate how long you have been pregnant and your due date.
sentences.chinese: 這可以幫助醫生評估你懷孕的日期以及預定產期。

sentences.english: I'm sorry, we have no record of a reservation in your name.
sentences.chinese: 對不起，沒有以您的名字預定的餐位。

sentences.english: Which class level would you like to enroll in?
sentences.chinese: 你預定想念哪一個程度的班別？

sentences.english: Do we have to pre-book tours, or can we get them on-site?
sentences.chinese: 我們是必須事先預定旅行，還是可以到那兒再說？

sentences.english: Some of those launches are expected to take place as early as this weekend.
sentences.chinese: 這是預定好的計畫只是提早到這星期實行。

sentences.english: All the tables by the window have been booked. I hope you will understand.
sentences.chinese: 所有靠窗的臺都已被預定了，希望您能諒解。

sentences.english: I was frantic to finish the report on schedule.
sentences.chinese: 我十萬火急地要按預定時間完成報告。

sentences.english: The development of the game has taken two years but advanced orders are impressive.
sentences.chinese: 開發製作該遊戲軟件長達兩年，但預定貨量十分喜人。

sentences.english: Hello, I'd like to reserve a single berth ticket from Shanghai to Beijing.
sentences.chinese: 你好，我想預定由上海去北京的單程臥鋪票一張。

sentences.english: English: How do I book a camping site?
sentences.chinese: 請問我應該怎樣預定一個宿營車位？

sentences.english: Review reserved tables and names of such; follow up on special arrangements for pre-assigned tables according to standards.
sentences.chinese: 查抄預定的桌子環境和客人姓名，跟進特別的擺設。

sentences.english: All the morning flights get being booked up.
sentences.chinese: 所有明早的飛飛機票都預定光了。

sentences.english: Warm and cosy private dining rooms are available - book early to avoid disappointment.
sentences.chinese: 舒適溫馨的單間接受預定服務，請提前致電。

sentences.english: Only those pre-booked on Malacca excursions may disembark.
sentences.chinese: 惟有已預定馬六甲上岸觀光活動的乘客方可下船。
